'''丹尼斯·帕內爾·蘇利文'''（{{lang-en|Dennis Parnell Sullivan}}，{{bd|1941年|2月12日}}<ref>{{Citation |chapter=Dennis Sullivan |chapterurl=http://books.google.com/books?id=yuGic0WClQ4C&pg=PR13#v=onepage&q&f=false |title=Graphs and patterns in mathematics and theoretical physics |first=Anthony |last=Phillips |page=xiii |editor-first=Leon Armenovich |editor-last=Takhtadzhi͡a︡n |location=Providence |publisher=AMS Bookstore |year=2005 |isbn=0821836668 |accessdate=2011-08-11 |archive-date=2020-08-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200801012914/https://books.google.com/books?id=yuGic0WClQ4C&pg=PR13#v=onepage&q&f=false |dead-url=no }}.</ref>），[[美國|美國]][[數學家|數學家]]。他在[[拓扑学|拓扑學]]（代數拓扑及幾何拓扑）以及動力系統理論方面的研究頗有建樹。他是[[紐約市立大學|紐約市立大學]]研究生院的阿爾伯特·愛因斯坦講座教授，也是[[纽约州立大学石溪分校|紐約州立大學石溪分校]]的教授，2022年获得[[阿贝尔奖|阿贝尔奖]]。<ref name=":0">{{Cite web |title=2022: Dennis Parnell Sullivan {{!}} The Abel Prize |url=https://abelprize.no/abel-prize-laureates/2022 |access-date=2022-03-23 |website=abelprize.no |archive-date=2022-03-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220323111559/https://abelprize.no/abel-prize-laureates/2022 }}</ref>

== 拓扑學方面的工作 ==
他在1963年從[[萊斯大學|萊斯大學]]數學系畢業，1966年在[[普林斯頓大學|普林斯頓大學]]獲得數學博士學位。他的博士論文《Triangulating Homotopy Equivalences》{{NoteTag|中文译作“三角化同伦等价”<ref>{{Cite web|title=2022年阿贝尔奖得主揭晓|publisher=中国工业与应用数学学会|url=https://csiam.org.cn/home/article/detail/id/1697.html|access-date=2022-03-27|work=|date=2022-03-24|archive-date=2022-04-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220401092520/https://csiam.org.cn/home/article/detail/id/1697.html}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=奖金约575万元，数学界“诺贝尔奖”今天仅授予他一人|work=科学网|url=https://news.sciencenet.cn/htmlnews/2022/3/476157.shtm|access-date=2022-03-27|date=2022-03-23|6=|author=韩扬眉|archive-date=2022-04-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220414210537/https://news.sciencenet.cn//htmlnews/2022/3/476157.shtm}}</ref>}}是在{{le|威廉·布勞德 (數學家)|William Browder (mathematician)|威廉·布勞德}}指導下完成的<ref name="NYT">{{cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2022/03/23/science/abel-prize-mathematics.html|title=Abel Prize for 2022 Goes to New York Mathematician|first=Kenneth|last=Chang|work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|date=2022-03-23|access-date=2022-03-23|archive-date=2022-03-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220323110725/https://www.nytimes.com/2022/03/23/science/abel-prize-mathematics.html|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{MathGenealogy|id=1472|title=Dennis Sullivan}}</ref>。1974至1977年，蘇利文在[[法國高等科學研究所|法國高等科學研究所]]擔任研究員<ref name="sbu-abel">{{cite web|title=Dennis Parnell Sullivan Awarded the 2022 Abel Prize for Mathematics|url=https://news.stonybrook.edu/university/dennis-parnell-sullivan-awarded-the-2022-abel-prize-for-mathematics/|access-date=2022-03-23|date=2022-03-23|website=[[Stony_Brook_University|Stony Brook University]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220324003919/https://news.stonybrook.edu/university/dennis-parnell-sullivan-awarded-the-2022-abel-prize-for-mathematics/|archive-date=2022-03-24|url-status=live}}</ref><ref name="ihes">{{cite web|title=Dennis Sullivan, Mathematician|url=https://www.ihes.fr/en/professeur/dennis-sullivan-2/|access-date=2022-03-23|website=[[Institut_des_Hautes_Études_Scientifiques|Institut des Hautes Études Scientifiques]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211122204026/https://www.ihes.fr/en/professeur/dennis-sullivan-2/|archive-date=2021-11-22|url-status=live}}</ref>。

